message: >-
  If you use this harness in research on AI-assisted software engineering,
  deterministic agent guardrails, or provenance-verified code generation,
  please cite it as below.
type: software
title: next-supabase-agent-harness
abstract: >-
  A deterministic agent harness for Next.js 16 + Supabase projects: Claude
  Code hooks that gate turn completion on a green validation chain,
  security-invariant lint rules, row-level-security isolation tests, an
  inline-citation provenance pipeline verified against a pinned corpus, and
  supply-chain-hardened CI.
